{"tid":1439712,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"和你飛日本","createTime":"2019-08-10T07:53:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T15:53:23.000Z","uid":113930,"like":10,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0d65511341a54b60e11bca5232f454fae5d702aa","tid":1439712,"uid":113930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:53:20.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n小弟下星期準備飛日本東京<br />\n抱著多一分力唔多，但少一分力就好少嘅心態想以前線裝束吸引到日本更多人嘅注意<br />\n進行真點和理非嘅無聲訴求<br />\n<br />\n計畫著上印有日文五大訴求嘅黑衫同拖個連儂喼去<br />\n但就未知帶眼罩頭盔唔知會唔會因為保安問題被拒入境<br />\n想問下有無熟知入境條例嘅巴絲可以解答下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eef9d1103261f922c743c2bd771920c1bcd8a2f3","tid":1439712,"uid":113930,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:56:03.000Z","msg":"預左呢個時候離開香港會被屌<br />\n<br />\n但女友留學完準備返嚟想過去接佢<br />\n<br />\n當畀小弟休息一個週末屌細力少少唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f75d727fab4c7c4f6bde6f30305f45a93248d9c","tid":1439712,"uid":113930,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:56:50.000Z","msg":"駛唔駛咁快負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfbf2f90ecf749a99ed90b968afe35dff3f90817","tid":1439712,"uid":43178,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:59:27.000Z","msg":"香港先叫入境條例<br />\n日本叫出入境管理及難民認定法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0fe7481da65c2433389d9e278f58da6d326a983","tid":1439712,"uid":182774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:04:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"25968d0e3a9c7711a27a091d27ba789c12c7a878","tid":1439712,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:05:39.000Z","msg":"緊急！關於港島東反送中反黑大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1439067